            "title": "盤中速報 - 集中市場加權指數下跌-604.39點至26821.97點，跌幅2.2%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間21日09:00，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌604.39點（或2.2%），暫報26821.97點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-1.71%</li><li>近 1 月：-0.95%</li><li>近 3 月：+16.09%</li><li>近 6 月：+27.41%</li><li>今年以來：+20.12%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Flash模組概念領跌-1.08%。其中    商丞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8277:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8277\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8277-TW</a>)            下跌        9.72%            ;        廣穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4973:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4973\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4973-TW</a>)            下跌        4.17%            ;        永崴投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3712:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3712\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3712-TW</a>)            下跌        2.69%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>運動服飾概念領跌-0.37%。其中    聚陽(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1477:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1477\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1477-TW</a>)            下跌        6.27%            ;        儒鴻(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1476:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1476\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1476-TW</a>)            下跌        2.77%            ;        威宏-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8442-TW</a>)            下跌        1.02%    。</p></section></main>",
